summary: The beta version of my first self-made Dungeon.
descriptionHtml:
NOT WORKING ON THIS ANYMORE! since I\'m getting bored with playing a lot of Skyrim...
This is the Beta stage of my Dungeon \"The Ruined Hideout\", Still gotta do a bit of cluttering, but I\'d like to share it with erveryone, before releasing the complete version.

You may use the Dungeon in your own works, but don\'t upload anything that has to do with this without asking me anything!

I have done the Navmeshing now, and there are a few NPC enemies walking around. Not all loot is quite finished yet, there will be more.

Any positive or negative comments/feedback is appreciated (especially the positive ones ofcourse!) and if you find any flaws, please message me about it and I\'ll try to fix it :)

Don\'t forget to endorse and have fun,
take care!
author: Jojo4u
